Name: autocreate_sieve_script_compile
Type: SWITCH
Default-Value: 0
Last-Modified: 2.5.0

If set to yes and no compiled sieve script file exists, the sieve script
which is compiled on the fly will be saved in the file name that
:imapdconf:`autocreate_sieve_script_compiled` option points to. In order
for a compiled script to be generated, :imapdconf:`autocreate_sieve_script`
and :imapdconf:`autocreate_sieve_script_compiled` must have valid values.
